===Etymology===
From {{etyl|enm|en}} {{m|enm|berd}}, from {{etyl|ang|en}} {{m|ang|beard}}, from {{etyl|gem-pro|en}} {{m|gem-pro|*bardaz}} (compare {{etyl|fy|-}} {{m|fy|burd}}, {{etyl|nl|-}} {{m|nl|baard}}, {{etyl|de|-}} {{m|de|Bart}}), from {{etyl|ine-pro|en}} {{m|ine-pro|*bʰardʰeh₂|*bʰardʰ-eh₂}} (compare {{etyl|la|-}} {{m|la|barba}}, {{etyl|lt|-}} {{m|lt|barzda}}, {{etyl|ru|-}} {{m|ru|борода́}}).

